{"tid":1646730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動Post] 十八區開花如何進化","createTime":"2019-10-11T12:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T01:40:30.000Z","uid":99964,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"204de05151296ddc21935449e67e498d2402ad27","tid":1646730,"uid":99964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"今日行街聽到個大叔講，拎上嚟討論下。<br />\n<br />\n自從黨鐵宵禁，十八區開花已經係不可改變嘅趨勢。但係開過幾日，裝修嘅伎倆對家已經唔係好怕。咁樣十八區開花點樣繼續落去好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議，每個區identify一個目標地點，例如係啲高官、議員、警犬嘅屋企附近，我哋係佢附近抗議，貼下文宣咁，等佢知道市民嘅不滿，俾啲壓力佢地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n利申：一定要合法和平，遊行集會記得申請不反對通知書啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bd716d09388795f222cfcdf8391c07eb273ac5","tid":1646730,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"突發！香城online現已公開發售！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b3a564b1a8c450cc4526edae13f71e1f9804ea0","tid":1646730,"uid":264128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"正式宣布 今晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c424cd3b0d78f8efde9286c791cb7c26a63b269","tid":1646730,"uid":99964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:26:26.000Z","msg":"自推一下先~"},{"pid":"cb1cb9c5f2932b1d51abd61a0c1541ae01d8e8ff","tid":1646730,"uid":99964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"再推一下~"},{"pid":"eba7766aa55a16c5d6605e4af14e1fa2fc74d02e","tid":1646730,"uid":99964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"